                        You (in your car) have a green light and want to turn right. A pedestrian is waiting to cross the street you want to turn into, and they have a "Walk" signal. What should you do?
                    </div>
                    <div class="scenario-options">
                        <div class="scenario-option" data-scenario="2" data-option="A">
