            <div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 25px; margin: 30px 0;">
                <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1.2rem;">üéØ Key Performance Insights</h3>
                <div style="color: #e5e7eb; line-height: 1.7;">
                    ‚Ä¢ <strong>Signal Timing:</strong> Always signal 100 feet or 3-4 seconds before turning<br>
                    ‚Ä¢ <strong>Right-of-Way Rules:</strong> Yield to pedestrians and vehicles on your right<br>
                    ‚Ä¢ <strong>Consistency:</strong> Use turn signals for every turn and lane change<br>
